-- ============================================
-- SEED: restore the 27 insurance/tax/notary services
-- ============================================
-- The public services page used to render this content from static i18n
-- keys + hardcoded icon components. That was replaced with a Supabase-backed
-- CRUD (src/views/admin/Service*.vue) but the table was never seeded, so the
-- public page currently reads an empty table and shows nothing.
--
-- This restores the original content into public.services, sourced directly
-- from src/i18n/es.json and src/i18n/en.json's "services.items.*" keys.
-- Icons were extracted from src/components/icons/*.vue into static files at
-- public/service-icons/<slug>.svg (no Supabase Storage upload needed for
-- these — they ship with the site).
--
-- Safe to run once. Skips rows whose slug already exists.

on conflict (slug) do nothing;
